text.tspan: I don't get told much about this thing.
I just call it "The Test" because I know
it is a result of a test, I just have no idea
which one. Whatever it was, it found
the ability to speak in its own language.
Just a repeated pattern of different
pitched sounds, but it knows what
it's saying. I only ever saw it once though.
They should really get somebody else
to write these ones, I have no idea what
